Its product categories include hair and skin care products, makeups, and fragrances. The company operates in Sweden, Norway, Finland, Denmark, Germany, the Netherlands, Poland, and Austria. Lyko Group AB (publ) was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Vansbro, Sweden.
